description: [``botocore``] Deprecated assignedValue property for actuators and attributes.  Added a message to invalid nodes and invalid decoder manifest exceptions.
[``botocore``] Doc-only update for CloudWatch Logs, for Tagging Permissions clarifications

[``botocore``] Link devices now support buffer size (latency) configuration. A higher latency value means a longer delay in transmitting from the device to MediaLive, but improved resiliency. A lower latency value means a shorter delay, but less resiliency.
[``botocore``] This release provides the approximate number of assets in a packaging group.
